👉 Have you ever tried to create factory farm images with AI and found them unrealistic?

The images in this post were created using Midjourney and serve as evidence that, regardless of the prompt, the creations do not accurately reflect how animals are transported or treated.

When prompt revision is disabled, the images reflect the reality of intensive farming, such as cows confined indoors and pigs on concrete floors behind barriers.🚫🐷

AI designed to reduce bias in the human case is creating misleading images of animal farming, hiding the suffering of sentient beings.💔
